data.description: Nestled in a prime location, this inviting 3-bedroom, 2-bathroom home offers the perfect blend of comfort and convenience. Situated within easy walking distance of schools and the vibrant heart of Burley, this residence boasts an open layout, a mostly fenced-in backyard, and a spacious 2-car garage. The well-designed open layout seamlessly connects the main living areas, creating a spacious and inviting atmosphere. Whether you're entertaining guests or spending quality time with family, this layout provides both flexibility and functionality. Three comfortable bedrooms provide plenty of space for rest and relaxation. The master suite features an ensuite bathroom for added privacy. Schedule a viewing today and envision yourself living in this charming residence.
